FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning ACOS-4 HTTP Cookie header has unknown format
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) (\S+).*a10logd: \[(\S+)\]<(\d+)> HTTP Cookie header has unknown format \(([^)]+)\):\s*(.*)
FastPattern.pattern: a10logd: \[ACOS\]<4> HTTP Cookie header has unknown format

FastField.defaultValue: HTTP Cookie header has unknown format

FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning ACOS-4 Cookie (overflow from above message)

FastField.defaultValue: HTTP Cookie header has unknown format

FastPattern.description: SystemStatus ACOS,AX-6 Service on virtual Server port
FastPattern.pattern: a10logd: \[A(?:COS|X)\]<6> Service \S+ on virtual [Ss]erver \S+ port \d+ is \w+

FastField.defaultValue: Service $5 on virtual Server $6 port $7 is $8

FastPattern.description: ServiceWarning AX-4 Virtual server service port connection limit exceeded
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) (\S+).*a10logd: \[(\S+)\]<(\d+)> Virtual server (\S+) service port (\d+) connection limit (\d+) exceeded
FastPattern.pattern: a10logd: \[AX\]<4> Virtual server \S+ service port \d+ connection limit \d+ exceeded

FastField.defaultValue: Virtual server $5 service port $6 connection limit $7 exceeded

FastPattern.description: SystemStatus HMON-6 SLB server port of group is up|down (message)
FastPattern.pattern: a10logd: \[HMON\]<6>.*?SLB server \S+ .*?\([.\d]+\) \S+ port \d+ of group \S+ is (?:up|down)

FastPattern.description: SystemStatus HMON-6 SLB server port of group is up|down (no message)
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) (\S+).*a10logd: \[(\S+)\]<(\d+)> SLB server (\S+) \(([.\d]+)\) (\S+) port (\d+) of group (\S+) is (up|down)\.
FastPattern.pattern: a10logd: \[HMON\]<6> SLB server \S+ \([.\d]+\) \S+ port \d+ of group \S+ is (?:up|down)\.

FastPattern.description: UserLogon SYSTEM-5 session for user has been opened

FastPattern.description: UserLogoff SYSTEM-5 Session ID for user has timed out

FastPattern.description: PolicyModify SYSTEM-6 User successfully saved the running configuration

FastPattern.pattern: a10logd: \[SYSTEM\]<6>.*?User "[^"]*" with session ID \d+ successfully saved the running configuration

FastPattern.description: PolicyModify SYSTEM-6 Running configuration successfully saved
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) (\S+).*a10logd: \[(\S+)\]<(\d+)>.*?Running configuration successfully saved to "([^"]*)" in Partition "([^"]*)" by user "([^"]*)" using Session ID (\d+)
FastPattern.pattern: a10logd: \[SYSTEM\]<6>.*?Running configuration successfully saved to "[^"]*" in Partition "[^"]*" by user "[^"]*" using Session ID \d+
